Package io.springlets.data.domain.jaxb

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GlobalSearchAdapter
    JAXB XmlAdapter to convert Springlets GlobalSearch instances into a SpringletsDataJaxb.GlobalSearchDto and vice versa.
    IterableAdapter<S>
    JAXB XmlAdapter to convert Iterable instances into a Collections and vice versa.
    OrderAdapter
    JAXB XmlAdapter to convert Spring Data `Order` instance into a SpringletsDataJaxb.OrderDto and vice versa.
    PageableAdapter
    JAXB XmlAdapter to convert Spring Data `Pageable` instance into a SpringletsDataJaxb.PageRequestDto and vice versa.
    PageAdapter
    JAXB XmlAdapter to convert Spring Data `Page` instance into a SpringletsDataJaxb.PageDto and vice versa.
    SpringletsDataJaxb
    Spring Data SpringDataJaxb clone to use public PageableAdapter class inside SEI interfaces.
    SpringletsDataJaxb.GlobalSearchDto
    The mutable DTO for GlobalSearchs.
    SpringletsDataJaxb.OrderDto
    The DTO for Sort.Order.
    SpringletsDataJaxb.PageDto
    The DTO for Page.
    SpringletsDataJaxb.PageRequestDto
    The DTO for Pageables/PageRequests.
